{"tid":1074133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【野宿】妻女探望劏房難容　清潔工一家寄居天橋：最緊要在一起","createTime":"2019-03-23T07:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T04:37:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d6fde1fe9004005b8231ef562ee51d54504ba1","tid":1074133,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"在鬧市行人天橋一隅，圓木椅、行李箱、木樓梯等家俱亂擱在花盆之間如同垃圾，十多個盆栽整齊排列成兩行，中間留有一條通道，陳女士稱那處為「門口」。花盆為門，泥土上的綠葉仿似是簾子，遮掩著後方的白色「小屋」。<br />\n途人對垃圾堆不屑一顧，這卻是陳女士一家三口「暫借」來共聚天輪的中途站，為何不租住房子呢？「租金太貴了，每晚要三四百元，我寧願把錢花在女兒身上，讓她吃飽，所以先暫時住在這裡。」<br />\n早前英國經濟學人智庫公佈2019年全球生活成本指數，香港跟巴黎及新加坡並列第一&mdash;&mdash;我們嘆息著物價高漲的同時，有一家三口甘願以街道為家，車聲為鄰，換取短暫團聚的時光。<br />\n當我們在「門口」張望時，有名束著辮子小女孩從屋子裡走出來，從後跟來的媽媽喊道：「不要走遠啊。」身穿黑色運動服的媽媽拿著裙子，跨過置在屋子前的木床架，打算跟女兒到附近的足球場廁所洗澡，然後再回來睡覺。<br />\n這晚是她們的第十夜。<br />\n46歲的陳女士跟女兒持旅遊證件從廣東來港，拜祭早前離世的家公，更重要的是與丈夫團聚。同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作，因半年前回鄉處理喪事而失掉長工，及後只能依靠一份清潔散工維生。陳女士和女兒還未來港時，丈夫獨自租住劏房度日；但房子難以擠下一家三口，丈夫便找來行人天橋上的屋子與家人團聚。<br />\n陳女士身型瘦削，樣子清秀，她蹲著床板上，說話時雙眼離不開在花盆間玩耍的女兒。十天前，她們還居於內地的房子，有電視、床鋪、浴室；但十天後卻睡在天橋上，陳女士搖著頭說：「沒辦法，在深水埗租房子一晚要四百多元，太貴了，我捨不得，寧可給女兒吃好一點。」她解釋，丈夫失掉長工後收入不穩定，未能負擔起劏房租金予一家三口居住。<br />\n丈夫輪班工作，工時每日十多小時，妻女正準備外出時，丈夫正在裡面休息。縱然睡在街頭，陳女士卻沒有一絲怨言，她微笑著說：「沒後悔，知道先生已經盡力了，他每日會給我們約三至四百元作生活費，他賺多少我沒有問。男人嘛，也要顧他的感受。」<br />\n<br />\n天橋遊樂場<br />\n每天早上八時多起床，陳女士用在公廁打來的清水洗面刷牙，然後帶女兒到附近的食店吃早餐後，下午有時跟女兒在公園遊玩，有時則讓她留在天橋上自娛自樂。一日只吃早晚兩餐，陳女士解釋說女兒食量少，她可以吃女兒剩下的飯餸。<br />\n女兒：「這裡太小了，我想回家。」<br />\n白天遊走街頭，晚上睡在天橋，陳女士對露宿的生活仍處之泰然，而女兒更視周旁的垃圾堆為遊樂場，途人為玩伴。女兒會躲在花盆間跟媽媽捉迷藏，或拿起地上的項鍊把玩，更不時逗途人說話。陳女士沒好氣地說：「有次途人拖著小狗經過，她就走上前問對方『我可以摸摸看嗎』？」天橋的環境於女兒眼中甚有新鮮感，但每當她回到屋子裡睡覺時，經常跟媽媽訴說想要回家。「媽媽我告訴你，這裡真的不好。」「為什麼不好呢？」「這裡太小了，我想回家。」<br />\n面對女兒的抱怨，陳女士收起笑容，垂下頭來呢喃說：「在這裡住，我也覺得不好意思，始終不是自己地方，對女兒也不好，如果仍沒有房子租得起，我們也會回去了。」<br />\n<br />\n長期病患 生活艱難<br />\n談到六歲大的女兒，陳女士總是面帶笑意，源於這一切得來不易。跟丈夫結婚後一年，陳女士懷上了女兒，但高齡產婦甚具風險，當年產子時更差點掉了性命。「生她的時候大量出血，差點難產，休養了很長時間，身體亦出現了問題。」陳女士說，在內地產子平均洗費約五、六千元，她卻花掉了四、五萬，「我現在有高血壓和糖尿病，要長期食藥，這幾年的生活的確較艱難。」<br />\n<br />\n「最緊要一家人在一起」<br />\n即使花了一筆金錢，但內地生活簡樸，陳女士與女兒的生活未算富裕，仍未愁吃住。可是，丈夫因工作連年身處異地，導致一家人長期分離；然而，妻女來港後能夠相聚，卻連基本的生活條件也不能滿足&mdash;&mdash;為何一家團聚的代價竟是流落街頭？矛盾如同一束死結，陳女士未懂得解決前，只能樂觀面對：「工作有不同階段，要給時間丈夫打拼，他說在香港有多點機會，能賺多點錢給家人。我們吃一點苦沒關係，最緊要一家人在一起。」<br />\n陳女士說丈夫工時長，需輪班工作，但每當放工後看見妻女總笑逐顏開。共聚天輪的時間短暫，陳女士計劃於月尾回鄉居住，讓女兒繼續上學，但這並非她所願：「如果解決到住的問題，我當然想留在香港，但長久住這裡都不是辦法，唯有回去。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2584994/org/3043b37c0ee1682902b604c433e62ad0.jpg/ijJA9KzOil6j3xaoAsmcLJLKmgUhtLuElOHpDZTh6Q0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2584994%2Forg%2F3043b37c0ee1682902b604c433e62ad0.jpg%2FijJA9KzOil6j3xaoAsmcLJLKmgUhtLuElOHpDZTh6Q0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=157289a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2580965/org/5455ada845bb5e0a4c88d2d5ef499c56.jpg/fY7wSeSE055PBm-JolOcibEcaKwZyvrYcCDY4HAg2OA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2580965%2Forg%2F5455ada845bb5e0a4c88d2d5ef499c56.jpg%2FfY7wSeSE055PBm-JolOcibEcaKwZyvrYcCDY4HAg2OA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e0de6b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳女士與女兒為了拜祭家公來港，但難以負擔房租就於天橋「暫居」十天。她最希望能一家團聚，礙於房租問題有機會再次跟丈夫分隔兩地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2580966/org/d7acfe44ca6f48885bf49c697311ced7.jpg/pj2kvVyHyp9Ovnixz57DSj9t4oARpKV_F6LGkBeixpA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2580966%2Forg%2Fd7acfe44ca6f48885bf49c697311ced7.jpg%2Fpj2kvVyHyp9Ovnixz57DSj9t4oARpKV_F6LGkBeixpA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ff3d78a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳太太每晚會到附近的足球場廁所洗澡及洗衣，之後便會回來睡覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2577758/org/4c568d3deb629088bc9dbbf4705a0501.jpg/w5EZFFeslnE1uIHuZs6hGHh6YEGKqG-B97uuLPe7riw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2577758%2Forg%2F4c568d3deb629088bc9dbbf4705a0501.jpg%2Fw5EZFFeslnE1uIHuZs6hGHh6YEGKqG-B97uuLPe7riw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=24b3d5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女兒對「新家」甚為好奇，她時常在花盆間遊玩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2577738/org/78c429b21d2dd13e979234bb7ca7f0de.jpg/bJMMOqqV169tR8laXv6_uS8Rrz20m8fLgAiG7oAIhu4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2577738%2Forg%2F78c429b21d2dd13e979234bb7ca7f0de.jpg%2FbJMMOqqV169tR8laXv6_uS8Rrz20m8fLgAiG7oAIhu4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6603a915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天橋旁堆積了不少雜物，但陳女士只帶了數件衣服過來，其餘的家具早已擱在這裡。"},{"pid":"c3d4542a7c4f52b671f35e48323b4a7ddfd4d90b","tid":1074133,"uid":228963,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcc27a31fbaab05c8be061583f0d9f2f3aeb5c7e","tid":1074133,"uid":53238,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"咁慘返上下啦<br />\n唔好落嚟啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b3aca3ca4e42819ca4fdd562e7dd0d0fa18ba6","tid":1074133,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"46歲的陳女士跟女兒持旅遊證件從廣東來港，拜祭早前離世的家公，更重要的是與丈夫團聚。同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作"},{"pid":"e21e2353d0c32a733645497f8c12dc0f675d44e6","tid":1074133,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b3b3aca3ca4e42819ca4fdd562e7dd0d0fa18ba6","tid":1074133,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"46歲的陳女士跟女兒持旅遊證件從廣東來港，拜祭早前離世的家公，更重要的是與丈夫團聚。同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"佢老公憑咩落到香港做野？老婆係大陸。<br />\n輸入專才？"},{"pid":"0313e0ee2d9443a2c889916a775a871994871ba1","tid":1074133,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e21e2353d0c32a733645497f8c12dc0f675d44e6","tid":1074133,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b3b3aca3ca4e42819ca4fdd562e7dd0d0fa18ba6","tid":1074133,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"46歲的陳女士跟女兒持旅遊證件從廣東來港，拜祭早前離世的家公，更重要的是與丈夫團聚。同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"佢老公憑咩落到香港做野？老婆係大陸。<br />\n輸入專才？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"探望去世的家公 <br />\n應該係男人老豆係香港人 申請個男人落黎"},{"pid":"ae613ad494d3404f290d66f2283ff419c1130953","tid":1074133,"uid":56123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e21e2353d0c32a733645497f8c12dc0f675d44e6","tid":1074133,"uid":17103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b3b3aca3ca4e42819ca4fdd562e7dd0d0fa18ba6","tid":1074133,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"46歲的陳女士跟女兒持旅遊證件從廣東來港，拜祭早前離世的家公，更重要的是與丈夫團聚。同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"佢老公憑咩落到香港做野？老婆係大陸。<br />\n輸入專才？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"清潔工專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7309007cddaac0953efe186975ebd42d18e4a977","tid":1074133,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"又係假故事呃恩恤安置"},{"pid":"6467749487a57aefae1aa8c68e053e0ea005901a","tid":1074133,"uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"同是40多歲的丈夫於兩年前隻身來港工作，因半年前回鄉處理喪事而失掉長工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個男人返工唔方勤力啦，如果勤力已經走左去做地盤"},{"pid":"9cd678e18a434403bec9f59ee5f5dd80aaf0680d","tid":1074133,"uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"我現在有高血壓和糖尿病，要長期食藥，這幾年的生活的確較艱難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好快會見到佢拎綜援每日唔洗錢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得香港咁on9移民黎之前唔洗驗身"},{"pid":"a03c214aca412200bf13632dd3ba2e03d8fa150c","tid":1074133,"uid":2126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"睇錯雞容"},{"pid":"9b50d31a09359dff47a8420777e884639f3d4013","tid":1074133,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZyRckN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZyRckN8.jpg&h=edea88c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ec2a7fdabb133adc26954c3590d280406b4cd9","tid":1074133,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁辛苦返大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那老雞同條小陰道喺到扮可憐博同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37565997b52c12f9803a5ed096c37cc81599d667","tid":1074133,"uid":18547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"雖然知好多都係扮野呃同情心，但見到堆相都會覺得可憐"},{"pid":"fb4061bb0077ac10603f738334543c153cbd1630","tid":1074133,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"上完新聞快上公屋"},{"pid":"7c9eb474eafa3a44cee4e04051f6bfaf03920e99","tid":1074133,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"去大陸網站報多啲"},{"pid":"7f608c649c57049b55a393f772ee27f26c5b7943","tid":1074133,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcc27a31fbaab05c8be061583f0d9f2f3aeb5c7e","tid":1074133,"uid":53238,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"咁慘返上下啦<br />\n唔好落嚟啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"咪就係"}]}